      "recovery_selfassessment_administrator_threats_bribes": "Staff do not use threats, bribes, or other forms of pressure to influence the behavior of program participants. Rate on a 5-point scale (1 = Strongly Disagree; 5 = Strongly agree)",
      "recovery_selfassessment_administrator_threats_bribes_opt_1": "1",
