      "recovery_selfassessment_administrator_staff_hopeful": "Staff believe in the ability of program participants to recover. Rate on a 5-point scale (1 = Strongly Disagree; 5 = Strongly agree)",
      "recovery_selfassessment_administrator_staff_hopeful_opt_1": "1",
